title: Pistorius
text: Pistorius or Pistor (from Latin "pistor" meaning <a href="miller">miller</a> or <a href="baker">baker</a>) are Latinized surnames, corresponding to the Dutch <a href="Bakker">Bakker</a> or the German <a href="Becker%20%28disambiguation%29">Becker</a>. Notable people with the surname include:
